items.badge_description: It's New Brew Thursday! Drink any beer you have never had before on three different Thursdays in a 20 day period.

Looking for more kick than a session beer, but want to be able to stay for a few rounds? You have to keep it in the middle. That's 80 beers with an ABV greater than 5% and less than 10%. Try 5 more for Level 17!

When a single isnâ€™t enough, make it a double. Doubling the hops and malts in a recipe results in a higher ABV and can pack quite a boozey punch. That's 20 different beers with the style that contains Imperial / Double in its style name. Try 5 more for Level 5!
Do you come from the land down under, where beer does flow, and men chunder? That's at least 100 different beers from Australia. Try 5 more for Level 21.
